<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-de.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-foundation-in-deutschland-portal/SCP-Logo-DE-500.png" style="width:200px;" alt="SCP-Logo-DE-500.png" class="image" />
